ady gets in a fight with a guy named peter over a girl. Peter plans to take revenge on Zach. Peters find Zach’s notebooks which hold every secret that happened in Zach’s life his name change his father even the people who threatened to kill them. Towards the end of the book peter decided to get zach in the worst trouble that he could ever imagine peter decided to tell the guy who tried to kill them everything he knew. He told them and they said they were going to give him 5,000 but turns out people aren’t always as they seem. Coming up towards the end Sam and Zach decided to capture all the men in the stage. Soon after this happens the grangers will have to be moved again so nothing happens to them. In the end of the book there’s a surprise ending that makes you think that family can conquered anything
