Katie MeaneyEnglish 3rdIRPZach’s Lie By: Roland Smith	Zach’s lie is a thrilling mind blowing book. It gives you a real life stories line that could actually happen to someone. This book I read got me really into it was I couldn’t put it down till I finished. Zach’s lie has 3 main parts in it. The 1st part of the book that I read is called Flight. It gives you depth information about the family what happen with jack’s father and how it’s going to change their lives forever. The stories line begins with jacks pretending to be a super hero and deciding to fall out a window and break both his legs which costed him about 3 months in the hospital. He said those 3 months brought him and his dad closer than ever and then his dad got a new job and was never home maybe once a week or twice. Then can you imagine you’re sleeping and a man puts tap over your mouth and says shh or I’ll kill you. he brings you down stairs where the rest of your family is laying on the couch tied up and taped mouths. The man that had captured you was a high class drug dealer. He threatens to kill you if you call the police. Soon after this all happens the men leave without saying a word the next day the police show up at your door tear apart your house and tell you that your husband is a drug dealer and got caught and is in jail. Know you guys are put understand service protection agency where you change your appearance, town and family. Your name is changed to jack Joanna and Patricia granger. You live in Elko Nevada and you own a minivan. You traded your high life nice cars lots of money and family for a rundown house small car and not a lot of money. In part 2 it’s called the three E’s which means everyone knows everything about everyone. In this part of the book Zach starts his new school at Elko Middle School. The first person he meets and becomes really good friends is the janitor whose name is Sam. Sam helps Zach with a lot of problems that he goes to not even the 2nd day of school Zach already gets in a fight with a guy named peter over a girl. Peter plans to take revenge on Zach. Peters find Zach’s notebooks which hold every secret that happened in Zach’s life his name change his father even the people who threatened to kill them. Towards the end of the book peter decided to get zach in the worst trouble that he could ever imagine peter decided to tell the guy who tried to kill them everything he knew. He told them and they said they were going to give him 5,000 but turns out people aren’t always as they seem. Coming up towards the end Sam and Zach decided to capture all the men in the stage. Soon after this happens the grangers will have to be moved again so nothing happens to them. In the end of the book there’s a surprise ending that makes you think that family can conquered anything
